## Recording Knowledge

### Failures (Record Immediately)
```bash
~/.claude/clc/scripts/record-failure.sh
```
Or create: `failure-analysis/YYYY-MM-DD-description.md`

### Successes
Create: `memory/successes/YYYY-MM-DD-description.md`

### Heuristics (Learned Patterns)
```bash
~/.claude/clc/scripts/record-heuristic.sh
```

### Experiments
```bash
~/.claude/clc/scripts/start-experiment.sh
```

