## First-Time Setup

Setup is automatic when you query CLC. If you see `[CLC_NEEDS_USER_CHOICE]`:

Use `AskUserQuestion` with options:
1. **Merge** (Recommended) - Keep existing config, add CLC
2. **Replace** - Use CLC only (backs up existing)
3. **Skip** - Don't modify (CLC features won't work)

Then run: `bash ~/.claude/clc/setup/install.sh --mode [choice]`

